1.0.name: wordpress/chrome-frame
1.0.description:
Google Chrome Frame (GCF) for Wordpress Admin / Backend. Dual Mode Plugin, can be used as a standard Plugin or as a Must-Use Plugin.

Features

  • Built upon the latest Google Chrome Technology.
  • A 2010 Core Developer Consideration (SF Camp 2010 code summit election).
  • Put force on your users to tell them who the Admin is.
  • Liberally Licensed under WTFPL.
  • Fixes a longtime Bug in WordPress.
  • Free.
